entry.title: greensock/GreenSock-AS2
entry.summary: Public repository for GreenSock's ActionScript 2 libraries like GSAP (TweenLite, TweenMax, etc.). For AS3, see the GreenSock-AS3 repository and for JavaScript, see the GreenSock-JS repository. Main site: http://www.greensock.com

entry.title: prefuse/Flare
entry.summary: Flare is an ActionScript library for creating visualizations that run in the Adobe Flash Player. From basic charts and graphs to complex interactive graphics, the toolkit supports data management, visual encoding, animation, and interaction techniques.

entry.title: flashgame/FiCharts
entry.summary: This is a Flash charts component based at as3 which can be used in web/Flash/Flex/AIR/etc. projects. It is beautiful and smart, easy to use, make data fly! you can find demo and documents at www.ficharts.com. hava any question mail to wallenEmail@gmail.com
